{
  "stem": "27340.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they didn't want to be reminded of the terrible things that were happening over on the continent.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And that quite honestly, even at the age of 13, was very painful, very painful, very, very painful.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Here we were, and suddenly those people who'd give us a haven, who'd saved our lives literally, didn't nevertheless want to know about the terrible things that were going on to not only our parents, our relatives, the Jewish people in general.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And Margate being more or less at the extension of the English Channel became, of course, very much a focal point during the evacuation of Dunkirk.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Hitl-- Chamberlain declared war at nine-- sorry, at 11 o'clock on that fateful Sunday morning, the 3rd of September, 1939.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the grace of God, my parents reached the shores, reached Britain 36 hours before Chamberlain declared war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Germany had already broken into Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The war was already raging in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they managed to get us into England 36 hours before the war started, an absolute miracle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so to finish that particular aspect of it, they both died a natural death here in England.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, indeed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at least they were out of Germany and they were safe and they were free.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as big as one can have it, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Certainly we had a very big reunion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My aunt and uncle were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, my parents were there, naturally, and my brother and myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was our family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, we feared for all the other many, many members who were left behind in Germany, yes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they came over here and were very much restricted as to how much money they were allowed to bring out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a pittance.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
